dct_title_s: [Industrial and railroad map of greater Kansas City]
dct_description_sm: Map showing the industries, transportation facilities, passenger stations, and freight stations of Kansas City. Includes lists of railroads and electric railways; legend also depicts interurban electric lines, streetcar lines, and switching limits, which are represented accordingly on the map. Alphabetical and numerical lists of industries are included as indexes.
prepared and published by Industrial Department, The Chamber of Commerce of Kansas City.
dct_creator_sm: Chamber of Commerce (Kansas City, Mo.), Industrial Dept.
